Subject: Services with service accounts
Description: Need to identify all server that has services running with AD service account. This is critical and I need 15 minute today to identify where the issue exist.
Solution_Comment__c:
Cause
Trying to identify all servers that has services running with a specific AD service account.

Resolution
The table contains a list of all services running on audited Windows servers, the statuse of each service, and which accounts are running them.

Job tree:
Windows > Privileged Accounts > Service Accounts > SG_ServiceAccounts > Results > ServiceAccounts
